  "StockRole": "Obsolete Superheavy",
  "YangsThoughts": "General Systems built exactly one of these right before the Amaris Civil War. SLDF wanted the biggest mech ever made and they wanted it to run without a pilot. That Drone Control System ate twenty tons and the whole project got written off as a failure. Then some poor mercenary scavengers dug it up in 3025 on an icy world and accidentally switched it back on. Took out everything in sight until someone found the control center and shut it down for good. After that they same group of mercenary buffoons ripped the Drone Control System out and converted it to manual controls, can't say it seemed worth the effort looking at it now.",
